==English==

===Adjective===

'''bleak'''

#Without color; pale; pallid.
#Desolate and exposed; swept by cold winds.
#Cold and cutting; cheerless; as, a bleak blast.
#A small European river fish (Leuciscus alburnus), of the family Cyprinidae; the blay.

